data.description: Located on an impressive golf course lot, with incredible mountain and sunset views in Sun City Grand! Original owners have maintained this home well, including newer windows, HVAC, and roof. Combined living room with formal dining area, den with built-in cabinets, Great Room that opens to the kitchen, & En-suite second bedroom complete the perfect floor plan. Kitchen offers separate islands, granite counters, and plenty of cabinetry. Numerous sliding glass doors from the living areas and master bedroom to the large backyard patios. Master suite offers a huge walk in closet and bathroom, complete with dual sinks, separate tub, and walk in shower. Community Features include a clubhouse, community pool, spa, pickleball & tennis courts, walking/bike paths, & fitness center. Welcome Home!
